      "data_i18n": null,
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "0 m/s",
          "is_correct": true,
          "data_i18n": null
        },
        {
          "text": "50pi/30 m/s",
          "is_correct": false,
          "data_i18n": null
        },
        {
          "text": "100pi/30 m/s",
          "is_correct": false,
          "data_i18n": null
        },
        {
          "text": "-50pi/30 m/s",
          "is_correct": false,
          "data_i18n": null
        }
      ],
      "explanation": "h(t) = 50sin^2(pi*t/30). h'(t) = 50 * 2sin(pi*t/30) * cos(pi*t/30) * (pi/30) = (100pi/30)sin(pi*t/30)cos(pi*t/30). At t = 15: sin(pi/2) = 1, cos(pi/2) = 0, so h'(15) = 0 m/s. The coaster is at peak height."
    },
